title: Load Break Switch
description: Maintenance activities for Load Break Switch in RMU system

# Load Break Switch


## Electrical

- Contact Resist.
- Hi-Pot Test


## Mechanical

- Timing Oper.
- Operating Force


## Insulation

- Ins. Resist.
- Dielectric Test


## Indication

- Mechanical Ind.
- Position Check
